ce:section.ce:para:
To investigate the morphology of CS/CMC/GQDs/ZnO@QUR nanocomposites, FE-SEM assessment has been used. The findings suggest that the nanocomposites have a nanoneedle structure (Fig. 2
                        ). The distribution of particle size of nanocomposites was studied by DLS analysis. As shown in Fig. 3
                        .a, the average particle size is 219.38 ± 5.21 nm, which is distributed in a spectrum between 171 nm and 300 nm. Also, the distribution of GQDs' particle size was investigated by DLS analysis. As shown in Fig. 3.c, the average particle size of GQDs is 7.99 ± 1.62 nm, which is distributed between 5.61 nm and 11.7 nm.
